Starscream enters the Predacon base, shocked by what the bot had said.

"MEGATRON bids you enter."

"Megatron? No it can't be him. He became Galvatron. Maybe it's that 
Megatron from when I took that Waspinator's body. I'll see soon 
enough."

He turns to the bot that told him to come in.

"Where may I find Megatron?"
